name: Lumina, Twilightsworn Shaman
desc: Once per turn: You can banish 1 "Lightsworn" monster from your hand or GY, then target 1 of your banished "Lightsworn" monsters, except "Lumina, Twilightsworn Shaman"; Special Summon it. Once per turn, if another of your "Lightsworn" monsters activates its effect: Send the top 3 cards of your Deck to the GY.
